      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor, superficial scratches and a few small stone chips on the hood typical of careful use. Inside, the cabin remains comfortable and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with all features functioning as intended and a consistent service history. It offers a smooth ride and represents a dependable option for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
