    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, the dual-VANOS system has been recently overhauled, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, transferring power through a factory M-Variable differential. The chassis is sorted with refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the sharp turn-in characteristics these cars are known for. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain and suspension remain in excellent operational health.",
